Class DefaultDataProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.operando.core.cpcu.questionnaires.DefaultDataProcessor
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ServiceDataProcessor

    public class DefaultDataProcessor
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class DefaultDataProcessor. This class will be heavily changed to be integrated into the actual system. This is so it can pull the data out of the live OPERANDO system and return them in the same manner. naturally, these woudnt use the file system but the databases.
